msgid ""
"The sum of the base allocations is 6, even though 7 constituencies must "
"be assigned. The correction awards the missing +1 to one of the parties "
"with an odd seat count (here B or C)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:30
msgid "Correction Strategy"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:32
msgid ""
"The missing +1 (or several, if multiple parties are affected) is awarded "
"according to a configurable strategy. Only parties with an **odd** seat "
"count are eligible, since only for them is a correction mathematically "
"justified."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "Strategy"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "`FAVOR_LARGE_PARTIES` *(default)*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "The party (or parties) with the most seats receive the +1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "`FAVOR_SMALL_PARTIES`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "The party (or parties) with the fewest seats receive the +1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "`PROPORTIONAL`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "Random, weighted by seat count (larger parties more likely)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "`PROPORTIONAL_REVERSED`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "Random, inversely weighted (smaller parties more likely)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "`RANDOM`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "Uniform random selection among parties with odd seat counts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "`NEGOTIATED`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md
msgid "An external callback function decides which parties receive the +1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:43
msgid ""
"In the example above with `FAVOR_LARGE_PARTIES`: B has more seats than C,"
" so B receives the +1 → B: 2, C: 0."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:45
msgid ""
"**Note**: The correction procedure also determines on a case-by-case "
"basis whether a party with only one seat may fill it with a constituency "
"representative."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:49
msgid "Effect of `constituency_representation`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:51
msgid ""
"This parameter (from the global configuration) controls which parties "
"receive constituencies at all:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:53
msgid ""
"**`ENTIRE_PARLIAMENT`** *(default)*: All parties receive constituencies "
"proportional to their seats."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/constituency_count_determination.md:54
msgid ""
"**`GOVERNING_MAJORITY`**: Only the governing parties receive "
"constituencies. The opposition receives 0 constituencies."
msgstr ""

